Load Region and Country Data to ODS: 10

 

Double click on the PackageLoadRegionCountry.dtsx. If it’s the first time, you will be presented with a blank pane on the Control Flow Task. 

·         Drag and drop 8 Data Flow Tasks from SSIS Toolbox on to the Control Flow Task for the 4 datasets and name them appropriately as shown in the screenshot below. 2 Data Flow Tasks per Dataset – one for region data and the other for country data from each Dataset linked with the Precedence Constraints.

 



 

·         Double click on the first Data Flow Task to configure the extraction of regions from the first dataset as below screenshot:

 

















 

·         Double click on the second Data Flow Task to configure the extraction of countries from the first dataset as below screenshot:
